nodes.title: About
widgets_values:
# Interfacial Workflow / Made by Project Soulstealer #

Interface: Variational/Seed Generation
Version: v1.0.1

This is the Advanced Workflow, with advanced prompter and more capable Plasma Noise Generator. Plasma allows your images to have deeper darks and brighter lights. Also allows you to get more out of your CLIP than usual. Also allows loading V-Prediction models. Also allows you to set your CLIP SKIP manually. Also have seed separately from the modules.

This workflow will generate 16 images at once, allowing you to quickly browse seeds.
0-0: Original image with specified seed.
1-0 .. 3-0: Seed of generation changed by +1, +2 or +3, seed of plasma noise unchanged
0-1 .. 0-3: Seed of generation unchanged, seed of plasma noise changed by +1, +2 or +3

Color Coding:
Cyan = Input nodes. You set information about what you want to those.
Yellow = Processing nodes. Don't touch those.
Green = Output nodes. This is where you get your result.
Black = Debug/Processing nodes. This is where you can see intermediate results.
